      *  ORDER DETAIL FILE <LOCAL PARTS PROCUREMENT SYSTEM>
     FAFAPL84 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===============================================================
      ** DELETE DUE DATE **
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A8SKHZ
     I                                        1   40A8SKYY
     I                                        5   60A8SKMM
     I                                        7   80A8SKDD
      ** SUMMARY DATE **
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A8SUHZ
     I                                        1   40A8SUYY
     I                                        5   60A8SUMM
     I                                        7   80A8SUDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140W@TIME
     I                                        1   60W@THMS
     I                                        1   20W@TH
     I                                        3   40W@TM
     I                                        5   60W@TS
     I                                        7  140W@DYMD
     I                                        7  100W@DY
     I                                       11  120W@DM
     I                                       13  140W@DD
      *===============================================================
      *  PARAMETER TRANSFER                                *
      *===============================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@HIN1  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN2  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@BOX   40
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           KEY01     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           P@HIN1
     C                     KFLD           P@HIN2
     C                     KFLD           P@HIN3
      *
     C                     TIME           W@TIME
     C           KEY01     SETLLAFAPL84
     C                     Z-ADD0         P@BOX
      *-------------------------
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY01     READEAFAPL84                  90
     C   90                LEAVE
     C*
     C           A8SKJY    IFEQ 'D'                        DELETE
     C           A8SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           A8SUPP    IFEQ *BLANK                     SUPPLIER
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
      ** SUMMARY DATE **
     C           A8SUHZ    IFNE 0
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         P@BOX
     C*
     C                     ENDDO
      *-------------------------
